            "body": "I don't believe that's the case. I think what they were referring to is `vim.lsp.diagnostic._enable` which is accessible but it's technically private. `vim.diagnostic.enable` just turns off the display of the diagnostics but doesn't prevent them from being requested (which is what we want to stop).\n\nOn top of that, we'd actually need `_refresh` from `vim.lsp.diagnostic` which is not exposed at all.",
